      <title>拜登向泽连斯基提供 2.25 亿美元援助，并为延迟道歉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/biden-gives-zelenskiy-225m-in-aid-apologizes-for-funding-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登在与乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基会晤时宣布了向乌克兰提供 2.25 亿美元新援助计划，并承诺在基辅寻求扭转与俄罗斯战争局势之际美国将继续提供支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-07/biden-gives-zelenskiy-225m-in-aid-apologizes-for-funding-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Jun 2024 11:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
